)</script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js" noModule=""></script></head><body class="__variable_f367f3 font-sans antialiased" style="font-family:var(--font-inter), system-ui, sans-serif"><div hidden=""><!--$--><!--/$--></div><!--$--><div class="min-h-screen bg-[#0a0a0a] text-gray-200"><nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-gray-800/50 bg-[#0a0a0a]/80 backdrop-blur"><div class="mx-auto flex h-16 max-w-5xl items-center justify-between px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><a class="flex items-center gap-2" href="/"><div class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500 to-brand-300"><span class="text-sm font-bold text-white self-end mb-1">D</span><span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-violet-700 self-end mb-2 ml-0.5 shrink-0"></span></div><span class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">Doable</span></a><a class="flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-gray-400 transition-colors hover:text-white" href="/"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-left h-4 w-4"><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"></path><path d="M19 12H5"></path></svg>Back to home</a></div></nav><div class="border-b border-gray-800/50"><div class="mx-auto flex max-w-5xl gap-6 overflow-x-auto px-4 py-3 text-sm sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><a class="whitespace-nowrap text-gray-400 transition-colors hover:text-white" href="/terms">Terms of Service</a><a class="whitespace-nowrap text-gray-400 transition-colors hover:text-white" href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a><a class="whitespace-nowrap text-gray-400 transition-colors hover:text-white" href="/cookies">Cookie Policy</a><a class="whitespace-nowrap text-gray-400 transition-colors hover:text-white" href="/acceptable-use">Acceptable Use</a><a class="whitespace-nowrap text-gray-400 transition-colors hover:text-white" href="/dmca">DMCA</a><a class="whitespace-nowrap text-gray-400 transition-colors hover:text-white" href="/contact">Contact</a></div></div><main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><article class="legal-article"><h1>Cookie Policy</h1><p class="text-sm text-gray-500"><strong>Last updated:</strong> April 27, 2026</p><p>This Cookie Policy explains how <strong>Doable Works LLC</strong> uses cookies and similar technologies on doable.me, dev.doable.me, and related services (the “Service”).</p><h2>What are cookies?</h2><p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They are widely used to make websites work, or work more efficiently, and to provide information to site owners.</p><h2>Cookies and storage we use</h2><h3>Strictly necessary (always on)</h3><p>Required for core functionality. Cannot be disabled without breaking the Service.</p><ul><li><code>doable_access_token</code> — short-lived authentication token (localStorage)</li><li><code>doable_refresh_token</code> — refresh token for renewing your session (localStorage)</li><li><code>doable_theme</code> — remembers your light/dark theme preference (localStorage)</li><li><code>doable_brand_theme</code> — remembers your brand color preference (localStorage)</li><li>OAuth state nonce — CSRF protection during OAuth login</li></ul><h3>Functional</h3><ul><li>UI preferences (sidebar collapsed, panel layout)</li><li>Recently opened projects</li><li>Editor settings (font size, key bindings)</li></ul><h3>Analytics</h3><p>We may use first-party analytics to understand how the Service is used and to improve it. We do not use third-party advertising trackers.</p><h3>Payment</h3><p>Stripe sets cookies on its own checkout pages for fraud prevention and session management. See<!-- --> <a href="https://stripe.com/cookie-settings" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Stripe’s cookie settings</a>.</p><h2>Managing cookies</h2><p>Most browsers allow you to view, delete, or block cookies. Blocking strictly necessary cookies will prevent the Service from functioning (you will not be able to sign in). You can clear locally stored data at any time via your browser settings.</p><h2>Do Not Track</h2><p>We do not currently respond to Do Not Track signals because no consistent industry standard exists. We do, however, honor opt-out requests described in our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p><h2>Changes</h2><p>We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. We will post the updated version on this page and update the “Last updated” date.</p><h2>Contact</h2><p>Questions? Email<!-- --> <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#5d2d2f342b3c3e241d39323c3f3138733038"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="58282a312e393b21183c37393a343d76353d">[email&#160;protected]</span></a>.</p><!--$--><!--/$--></article></main><footer class="border-t border-gray-800/50"><div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><p class="text-xs text-gray-600">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Doable Works LLC. All rights reserved. Doable is a registered service of Doable Works LLC.</p></div></footer></div><!--/$--><script data-cfasync="false" src="/cdn-cgi/scripts/5c5dd728/cloudflare-static/email-decode.min.js"></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/webpack-392064f454473ca7.js" async=""></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"1:\"$Sreact.fragment\"\n2:I[82991,[\"7177\",\"static/chunks/app/layout-43c097e5cd8aedfd.js\"],\"TracingInit\"]\n3:I[48984,[],\"\"]\n4:I[16303,[\"8039\",\"static/chunks/app/error-1624ed23f152bc29.js\"],\"default\"]\n5:I[8270,[],\"\"]\n6:I[43849,[\"3849\",\"static/chunks/3849-c0424a57e6cb463a.js\",\"4878\",\"static/chunks/app/(legal)/layout-ccaaeb65f7084f7e.js\"],\"\"]\n7:I[85112,[],\"OutletBoundary\"]\na:I[98400,[],\"AsyncMetadataOutlet\"]\nc:I[85112,[],\"ViewportBoundary\"]\ne:I[85112,[],\"MetadataBoundary\"]\n10:I[58567,[],\"\"]\n:HL[\"/_next/static/media/e4af272ccee01ff0-s.p.woff2\",\"font\",{\"crossOrigin\":\"\",\"type\"